title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 646-9.5 - Exemptions
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 646-9.5 - Exemptions

State Regulations

Compliance with this Subpart shall not apply to: (a) Any person who has entered into or is
subject to a written agreement with the Commission which provides for the
substantial equivalent of the protections described in this Subpart. Notes
